latestIgtvVideos.title: 5 ways to style a Traditional Jacket.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Here's my 1st styling video. Most garment pieces were picked from my mom's wardrobe. I went for white and blue combination with silver accessories, for a subtle yet stylish look which will make you stand out of crowd. Yes drapes are safe if pinned properly. but completely depends on your comfort, replace it with crop top of your choice.😊 Look1: Jackets × White kurta, Striped Pants with silver Jhumka.
Look2: Jacket × white blouse or dupatta draped as a blouse, striped pants with silver chocker.
Look3: Jacket × Skirt, white blouse or dupatta draped as a blouse with white plazzo with silver earring.
Look 4: ReversedJacket × Jumpsuit and earrings.
Look 5: Jacket × Jumpsuit(knotted)
plazzo, silver necklace and Jhumka.☺️

.

The journey was not easy peasy lemon squeezy but there was passion and devotion to fulfill the dream, which kept her going. Watching me stand with award  for Graduation Project,
Little Ananya would be so proud.
This post dedicated to her.
